Class Config.ImageMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirl.Config.ImageMarker
  • Enclosing class:
    Config

    public static class Config.ImageMarker
extends java.lang.Object
    An ImageMarker indicates an area of interest on an image, usually as a red circle annotation on the image. Also used to hold position information for pinned signals on floorplans.
